        {
            "title": "A股收跌   深股曾破萬點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股收跌，深股一度跌破萬點關，一周累計滬股跌0.5%，深股跌逾1%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20190507_FI_A股_FB-1-2-3-1-5_source-ap_-2-1-1-3.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20190507_FI_A股_FB-1-2-3-1-5_source-ap_-2-1-1-3.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬綜指收跌2點或0.07%，報3359點，今早開報3358點，跌4點或0.12%，早段高見3370點，升8點或0.24%，為全日高位，全日最低見3357點，跌5點或0.15%，成交4108.73億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">一周計累跌17點或0.5%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指收跌46點或0.47%，報10005點，今早開報10039，跌12點或0.12%，最高見10084，升33點或0.33%，其後反覆向下，臨近收市跌破萬點，報9998點，跌53點或0.53%，為全日低位。全日成交6568.13億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">一周計累跌117點或1.16%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300收升3點或0.09%，報3846點，創業板指數收跌16點或0.83%，報2009點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15026276-a%e8%82%a1%e6%94%b6%e8%b7%8c-%e6%b7%b1%e8%82%a1%e6%9b%be%e7%a0%b4%e8%90%ac%e9%bb%9e",
