            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">台灣股市靠穩。加權指數收市報22045點，升42點，升幅0.19%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">指數本周累計跌約0.12%。</p>\n</div>",
