        {
            "title": "半日收市｜港股半日升266點   泡泡瑪特遭沽售",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股半日升266點，中資金融股成升市功臣，泡泡瑪特(09992)遭拋售，成交居首。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250401_FI_source-web_09992-00041.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250401_FI_source-web_09992-00041.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數半日報23504，升266點或1.15，今早報23291，升53點或0.23%，已為半日低位，隨即節節向上，臨近半日收市高見23516，升279點或1.2%，為半日高位。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數半日升36點或0.71%，報5124點，今早開報5103，升15點或0.3%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生國企指數半日報104點或1.24%，報8515點，今早開升18點或0.22%，報8429點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指半日升1.11%或257點，報23486，低水19點 ; 恒生科技指數升32點或0.63%，報5121點，低水3點，國指期貨升98點或1.17%，報8503點，低水12點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市成交929.88億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">泡泡瑪特(09992)半日跌5.23%，報235.6元，人民日報發文籲管制盲盒，此外公司主打Labubu在二手市場價格腰斬。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">李寧(02331)半日漲6.8%，報16.02元，是表現最好藍籌，獲非凡領越(00933)增持，非凡領越半日升22.06報0.415元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中資金融股成升市主力。中國人壽(02628)升4.28%，報18.5元；中國平安(02318)升3.15%，報47.45元；工商銀行(01398)升3.15%，報6.22元；建設銀行(00939)升2.94%，報7.7元；招商銀行(03968)升2.78%，報53.6元；中國銀行(03988)升2.01%，報4.56元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">信義系捱沽，信義玻璃(00868)跌1.36%，報7.24元，為表現最差藍籌股 ; 信義光能(00968)跌0.84%，報2.35元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15025799-%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%bd%9c%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e5%8d%87266%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b3%a1%e6%b3%a1%e7%91%aa%e7%89%b9%e9%81%ad%e6%b2%bd%e5%94%ae",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-8.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-06-20 12:50:28",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "滬深股市半日個別發展",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地股市半日走勢不一。固態電池、腦機接口、光伏、白酒股等上升，但短劇遊戲股下跌。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證指數報3364點，升2點，升幅0.08%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成份指數報10032點，跌19點，跌幅0.19%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數先升後跌，報2015點，跌11點，跌幅0.56%。</p>\n</div>",
